high_descs: Pick up the dirty rag from the counter.
Wash the dirty rag in the sink with water.
Bring the rag to the toilet.
Put the rag on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag on the toilet tank lid.

high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the toilet, and then turn left to face the sinks.
Pick up the dirty purple towel in between the sinks.
Head towards the sink on your right.
Wash the dirty towel in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn around and head towards the toilet.
Place the towel on the left of the cardboard roll on the toilet basin.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean towel on the toilet basin.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn left, toward the counter between the two sinks.
Pick up the rag from between the sinks.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Turn around and go to the right side of the toilet.
Place the rag on the back of the toilet, to the left of the cylinder.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag on the back of the toilet.
